"...Guess I've been kicked out." [l][r]
[r]Gazing up at the dark sky, I mutter to myself. I feel lonely. Yeah, definitely lonely. [l][r]
Being alone is lonely. Having to lie is lonely. Being lied to is lonely too. [l][r]
[r]Lonely, lonely, sashimi, sushi. [l][r]
...I suddenly crave fish. [r]
No, that's not it. I want to eat sushi, but...[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

