"What's wrong, feeling sick?" [l][r]
...No, it was my classmates from the seminar. But right now, their innocent voices felt a bit comforting. [l][r]
[r]"Eh... heh. I had a fight with Chi-chan and got kicked out." [l][r]
I mixed a bit of truth and managed to lie convincingly. [l][r]

[cm] "Ah... a lover's quarrel with Minase-san?" [l][r]
"A couple's fight, huh?" [l][r]
"Yeah. It happens sometimes." [l][r]
Everyone said lightly, trying to comfort me. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

